= MODULE

sysadmin

= DESCRIPTION

This is the sysadmin module.
Configure a system administrator account for (potentially) several  users

== Supported Platforms

* Debian
* Redhat and others: not  tested yet)

== Main classes

* sysadmin($login, $groups, $ensure) :: Install and configure sysadmin

== Sample Usage

     import sysadmin
     [...]
     class { 'sysadmin':
           login   => 'localuser',
           ensure  => 'present',
     }

